                        <img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/home,features,cognitive-services,translator-text-api.svg" />
                        <h2>文本翻译 API<span>Translator Text API</span></h2>
                        <h4>通过简单的 REST API 调用即可轻松进行实时文本翻译</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="translator-text_1rmb-trial">申请试用<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em>
